import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
Vue.use(Router)
// 为Exam01.vue组件指定访问路径
// 在router.js引入组件
import Exam from "./components/Exam/Exam.vue"
import Exam01 from "./components/Exam/Exam01.vue"
import Exam02 from "./components/Exam/Exam02.vue"
import Exam03 from "./components/Exam/Exam03.vue"
import Exam04 from "./components/Exam/Exam04.vue"
import Exam05 from "./components/Exam/Exam05.vue"
import Exam08Fa from "./components/Exam/Exam08Fa.vue"
import Home from "./components/message/Home.vue"
import MessageList from "./components/message/commen/MessageList.vue"
import Login from "./components/xz/Login.vue"
import Index from "./components/xz/Index.vue"
import Product from "./components/xz/Product.vue"
import Selcart from "./components/xz/Selcart.vue"
// 为组件指定访问路径 /Exam01
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/Exam',component:Exam},
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Exam02',component:Exam02},
    {path:'/Exam03',component:Exam03},
    {path:'/Exam04',component:Exam04},
    {path:'/Exam05',component:Exam05},
    {path:'/Exam08Fa',component:Exam08Fa},
    {path:'/Home',component:Home},
    {path:'/MessageList',component:MessageList},
    {path:'/Login',component:Login},
    {path:'/Index',component:Index},
    {path:'/Product',component:Product},
    {path:'/Selcart',component:Selcart}
  ]
})
